    },
    {
      "id": "6a0655d00000000000e587bb",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/0cced7865f30c3b2ffea509ff50c34d9]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800081,
      "updated": 1778800081
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0655d00000000000e587bc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800081,
      "updated": 1778800081
    },
    {
      "id": "6a06561d0000000000e587c3",
      "text": "ざつまと申します。井戸端の皆さん、よろしくお願いします！",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800159,
      "updated": 1778800194
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16339b0000000000794800",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779839900,
      "updated": 1779839900
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a6c6e000000000001ebdf",
      "text": "role:",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781165167,
      "updated": 1781165171
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a6c45000000000001ebdd",
      "text": " Cosenseファンかつデライトフリーク",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781165126,
      "updated": 1781165172
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a6c45000000000001ebde",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781165126,
      "updated": 1781165126
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16339b0000000000794801",
      "text": "共同日記に書きそうなこと",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779839900,
      "updated": 1779839931
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1633a50000000000794802",
      "text": " webツールについて",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779839910,
      "updated": 1779839935
    },
    {
      "id": "6a275b1100000000007df7d6",
      "text": " インターネットやインディーウェブ的なものについて",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1780964113,
      "updated": 1781165097
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1633b60000000000794803",
      "text": " 他の場所で見つけたweb記事や動画のリンク",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779839926,
      "updated": 1781189381
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2acb040000000000e3f337",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781189382,
      "updated": 1781189384
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2acb070000000000e3f338",
      "text": "その他",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781189384,
      "updated": 1781189392
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2acb0f0000000000e3f339",
      "text": " 古いページの蒸し返しに興味があります",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781189392,
      "updated": 1781189402
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0656230000000000e587c4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800164,
      "updated": 1778800164
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0655d00000000000e587bd",
      "text": "Cosense歴",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800081,
      "updated": 1778800093
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0655e40000000000e587c0",
      "text": " 2017年？〜",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800102,
      "updated": 1778800116
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0655f30000000000e587c1",
      "text": "  もっと前からな気もするけど記憶に自信なし ",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800116,
      "updated": 1778800153
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0656460000000000e587c5",
      "text": " 非公開個人Cosenseが基本",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800199,
      "updated": 1778801938
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0657600000000000322e6d",
      "text": "  グループCosenseだと自分の家族向けのものを運営",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800482,
      "updated": 1778800519
    },
    {
      "id": "6a06565b0000000000e587c6",
      "text": "  あと一時的なプロジェクト向けに作った3, 4名規模のCosenseに参加してたこともあった",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800221,
      "updated": 1778801973
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0657ab0000000000322e6e",
      "text": "  2桁を飛ばして3桁memberのプロジェクトは初めてです",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800556,
      "updated": 1778800591
    },
    {
      "id": "6a066587000000000006fba1",
      "text": " 公開Cosenseとデライト",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778804104,
      "updated": 1778804348
    },
    {
      "id": "6a066563000000000006fba0",
      "text": "  [脱Twitter]の一環として情報出力を公開Cosenseに集約しようとするも、読まれてる気配の伝わってこなさに挫折",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778804069,
      "updated": 1778804177
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0665d1000000000006fba2",
      "text": "  2024年末から[デライト]をメインツールとして利用し始め、SNS的にも個人知識管理用途にも使っています",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778804178,
      "updated": 1778804268
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0d9ec500000000004c5c30",
      "text": "   [デライト.icon] https://dlt.kitetu.com/KNo.FD7E",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779277510,
      "updated": 1779277521
    },
    {
      "id": "6a066633000000000006fba3",
      "text": "  職業関連のことはデライトには書きたくないのもあり、そちらではCosenseを継続中",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778804277,
      "updated": 1779882805
    },
    {
      "id": "6a06665a000000000006fba4",
      "text": "   infoboxの強力さは手放せない",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778804316,
      "updated": 1779882799
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0658e60000000000322e70",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800872,
      "updated": 1778800872
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0655dd0000000000e587bf",
      "text": "井戸端について",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800094,
      "updated": 1778800098
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0656860000000000e587c8",
      "text": " 頻度に波はあるもののROM専として見ていました",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800263,
      "updated": 1778800309
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0656af0000000000322e65",
      "text": " 面白いサービスや製品を井戸端で知ることも多いので助かっています",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800305,
      "updated": 1778800349
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0656af0000000000322e67",
      "text": "  最近は[rururu]が個人的ヒット",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800305,
      "updated": 1778800351
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0656af0000000000322e68",
      "text": " Cosenseに新機能が実装されたときも真っ先に見に来ています",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800305,
      "updated": 1778800337
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0657350000000000322e69",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800439,
      "updated": 1778800439
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0657360000000000322e6a",
      "text": "参加のきっかけ",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800439,
      "updated": 1778800443
    },
    {
      "id": "6a06573a0000000000322e6b",
      "text": " 大きめのグループCosenseに参加する予定が出てきた",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800443,
      "updated": 1778800721
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0657450000000000322e6c",
      "text": " まずは賑わいのある井戸端で大規模グループCosenseの感触を掴んでおきたい",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800455,
      "updated": 1778800729
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0655d20000000000e587be",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1778800084,
      "updated": 1778800084
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0d9eb900000000004c5c23",
      "text": "参加中",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779277498,
      "updated": 1779679629
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13c18c0000000000ecbf43",
      "text": " [/delite]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779679629,
      "updated": 1779679631
